Master regulator identfication using VIPER

鉴定生命过程中的关键调控因子（Master Regulotr，MR）是了解生命动态变化的重要手段，VIPER是该领域流行的分析软件。本文档简单示例了VIPER的基本用法，更详细的例子见VIPER使用文档。

输入文件

library("viper")
library("bcellViper")
library(ggplot2)
data(bcellViper, package = "bcellViper")
regulon
Object of class regulon with 621 regulators, 6249 targets and 172240 interactions

读入表达谱：

load("/sibcb2/bioinformatics/Projects/VIPER/GSE45838/GSE45838_Symbol.RData")
colnames(ExS) = sapply(strsplit(colnames(ExS), "_"), function(z) z[1])
NTsample = c("GSM1116380", "GSM1116381", "GSM1116382")
KDsample = c("GSM1116383", "GSM1116384", "GSM1116385")
Ex = ExS[, c(NTsample, KDsample)]
colnames(Ex) = c(paste0("NT_R", 1:3), paste0("BCL6_R", 1:3))

关键调控因子

我们的测试数据来自GSE45838，我们比较了BCL6敲低样本和正常样本之间的差别。按照期望，BCL6被抑制的调控因子之一。

BCL6 = Ex[, 4:6]
NT = Ex[, 1:3]
signature = rowTtest(BCL6, NT)
signature <- (qnorm(signature$p.value/2, lower.tail = FALSE) *sign(signature$statistic))[, 1]
nullmodel = ttestNull(BCL6, NT, per = 1000, repos = TRUE, seed = 1, verbose = FALSE)
mrs <- msviper(signature, regulon, nullmodel = NULL, verbose = FALSE, pleiotropy = TRUE)
options(repr.plot.width=6, repr.plot.height=10, repr.plot.res = 200)
plot(mrs, 20, cex = .7)

转录因子的活性

tfMx <- viper(Ex, regulon, dnull = NULL, method = "rank", verbose = FALSE, pleiotropy = TRUE)
tfMx["BCL6", ]
    NT_R1     NT_R2     NT_R3   BCL6_R1   BCL6_R2   BCL6_R3 
 2.610084  3.456618  1.969055 -2.344552 -2.004593 -2.283521 
tfVx <- apply(tfMx[, 4:6], 1, mean) - apply(tfMx[, 1:3], 1, mean)
head(sort(tfVx))

同关键调控因子的分析一致，BCL6排名第二。
